{"tid":1473078,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"眾議員議長佩羅確定在未來數星期籌備通過《香港人權及自由法案》，並且禁止售賣子彈及防暴裝備給香港警察。","createTime":"2019-08-14T17:54:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T00:46:59.000Z","uid":62011,"like":74,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"921759604f82b19e321849cef726b9571891062c","tid":1473078,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:54:37.000Z","msg":"Pelosi Statement on Escalating Violence Against the People of Hong Kong<br />\nAUGUST 13, 2019<br />\n<br />\nSan Francisco &ndash; Speaker Nancy Pelosi issued this statement on the escalating violence perpetrated against pro-democracy protestors by the Chinese authorities in Hong Kong:<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;For ten weeks now, the people of Hong Kong have inspired the world with the courage and determination with which they are fighting for the freedom, justice and true autonomy that they were promised. The Chief Executive and Legislative Council must finally, fully meet the legitimate democratic aspirations of the Hong Kong people, as guaranteed under &lsquo;One Country, Two Systems,&rsquo; starting by completely and immediately withdrawing the dangerous extradition bill, investigating and ending police violence and granting universal suffrage.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;The escalating violence and use of force perpetrated against the Hong Kong protestors is extremely alarming. The pro-Beijing Chief Executive and the Hong Kong police forces must immediately cease the aggression and abuse being perpetrated against their own people.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;We urge President Trump to walk away from his recent statements, which invite miscalculation, and to work to advance peace, justice and democracy in Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;In the Congress, Democrats and Republicans continue to stand united with the people of Hong Kong in demanding the hopeful, free and democratic future that is their right. In the coming weeks, we will work to pass the bicameral and bipartisan Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act to reaffirm the U.S. commitment to democracy, human rights and the rule of law in the face of Beijing&rsquo;s crackdown and focus on banning the sale of munitions and crowd control gear to the Hong Kong police force.</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;If America does not speak out for human rights in China because of commercial interests, we lose all moral authority to speak out elsewhere.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"71f263f94fbcbdecd57928cd9e2fea7c09c4f964","tid":1473078,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:55:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.speaker.gov/newsroom/81319/?fbclid=IwAR1mZ56qrHpG2zkrpmbSfyjxSmU5lm3yhxBqXc5JS31QMMloMZg5IfGOOhI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.speaker.gov%2Fnewsroom%2F81319%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1mZ56qrHpG2zkrpmbSfyjxSmU5lm3yhxBqXc5JS31QMMloMZg5IfGOOhI&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQegzaf%2B7McJKZiP%2F5rhSwlYLA%3D&h=329265c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.speaker.gov/newsroom/81319/?fbclid=IwAR1mZ56qrHpG2zkrpmbSfyjxSmU5lm3yhxBqXc5JS31QMMloMZg5IfGOOhI</a>"},{"pid":"17fdbdb231b97f1f53aedecaf4d340c8256da156","tid":1473078,"uid":71713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:55:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c116d1d1180f7065adf1595d2d9d131faaa0d39","tid":1473078,"uid":105905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:55:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9554e2fd2cc61736ee55acbcad2f9df7253d5a22","tid":1473078,"uid":200971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:56:01.000Z","msg":"快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\